[[File:HujMatRug.jpg|thumb|A Huj mat rug]]

A '''Huj mat''' was a type of hand-woven [[Carpet/Legends|rug]] that, at first glance, appeared to be a jumble of colors and shapes with no definitive pattern. At close inspection, however, a subtle pattern was visible. This led to the common expression "see the pattern on the Huj mat".

